{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It sounds so strange because it was no reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the reasons we went [INAUDIBLE] the first to Terezin was because this lady, Green, or whatever her name was, did some blackmail with the stuff that she got for the children, rationings of food.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, of course, the German logic was, throw the whole orphanage into the camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we then went to Terezin when the Czech population was still there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's also not so agreeable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot remember, but we were punished for the silliest actions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to kneel down and stay the night kneeling and all these-- it sounds incredible, really incredible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's why, really, I almost wiped out of my memory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only remember it was very bad, and I was really relieved when we came into the children's home of Terezin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it develops the character of the neighbor, if you want it or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden you are not allowed to say, hello, or you are not-- and all these things, which I know now, of course, I was a child and didn't know, but I think this is even worse then the camps themselves.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You find a modus vivendus afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it takes some time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this here, you didn't know what to expect the next day, or the next second.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were thrown into this goyish world, all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were not your friends anymore, not your neighbors, they were scared and this is quite--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around the area, I mean, generally speaking about the whole-- before you come into the camp, before you were thrown together with your own-- it was quite hard, I think, for the grownups, even more.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
